# FAQ Schema Template

## JSON-LD Structure

Use this template to generate FAQ schema markup for each category page.

```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "{{QUESTION_1}}",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "{{ANSWER_1_PLAIN_TEXT}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "{{QUESTION_2}}",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "{{ANSWER_2_PLAIN_TEXT}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "{{QUESTION_3}}",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "{{ANSWER_3_PLAIN_TEXT}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "{{QUESTION_4}}",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "{{ANSWER_4_PLAIN_TEXT}}"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
