      }
    }
  ]
}
```

---

## Schema Rules

### Text Formatting
- Remove all markdown formatting (no **, no ##, no bullet points)
- Convert bullet lists to comma-separated text
- Keep answers under 300 characters for optimal display
- Use plain quotation marks, not smart quotes
- Escape any special characters

### Example Transformation

**Markdown Answer:**
```markdown
A white label casino is a pre-built online gambling platform provided by a third-party vendor. The provider handles:
- Licensing
- Software
- Games
- Payment processing

This allows operators to launch in 4-8 weeks.
```

**Schema Text:**
```
A white label casino is a pre-built online gambling platform provided by a third-party vendor. The provider handles licensing, software, games, and payment processing. This allows operators to launch in 4-8 weeks.
```

