## Validation

Before finalizing schema:

1. **Validate JSON syntax** at https://jsonlint.com/
2. **Test structured data** at https://search.google.com/test/rich-results
3. **Check character limits** - answers should be under 300 chars for best display
4. **Verify no HTML/markdown** remains in text fields
5. **Confirm questions match H3 headings** exactly in the content

---

## Implementation Notes

### Placement
Schema should be placed in the `<head>` section of the category page, or in a `<script type="application/ld+json">` tag before the closing `</body>`.

### One Schema Per Page
Each category page gets one FAQPage schema containing all 5-7 questions for that category.

### Updates
When FAQ content is updated, the schema must also be updated to match.
